	<section>
	    <h2>Post Office's within the <abbr title="United Kingdom">UK</abbr></h2>

	    <h3><a href="https://osm.mathmos.net/postoffice/" title="Post Office comparison tool">Analysing UK Post Office Data in OpenStreetMap</a></h3>

	    <p>
	    The above tool takes <a href="https://postoffice.co.uk" title="The Post Office, UK">Post Office</a> data stored by Open Street Map
	    (<abbr title="Open Street Map">OSM</abbr>) and compares it to an officially released data set from the Post Office, allowing for
	    the ability to see if data stored by <abbr title="Open Street Map">OSM</abbr> is accurate.
	    </p>

	    <p>The data made available by the post office includes post office names, addresses and opening hours.</p>
	</section>
